data.description: Introducing 10020 Whittle Ct, nestled on a private lot in White Plains, Maryland. As you approach, a long driveway welcomes you to this meticulously maintained residence, offering both curb appeal and a sense of seclusion. Step inside to discover a beautiful interior featuring a blend of carpet and wood flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. The main level features an open living area and kitchen kitchen, providing both functionality and style. With four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home provides ample space for comfortable living. The finished basement adds an extra layer of versatility, offering a free room that can easily transform into an additional bedroom, a personalized theater room, or any space to suit your lifestyle needs. The property's charm extends beyond its interiors, as the private lot provides a serene backdrop for outdoor activities and relaxation. Whether entertaining guests or enjoying quiet moments, the outdoor spaces offer endless possibilities. This well-kept home, with its modern features and flexible spaces, invites you to experience the perfect blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make 10020 Whittle Ct your next home sweet home.
